ContentDesc_Castrum Meridianum - Praetor: With the magitek field now out of commission, the path to the Ultima Weapon lies open. While the Immortal Flames sweep Castrum Meridianum and suppress the remnants of the enemy garrison, the Enterprise will bear you to the Praetorium, where you and your comrades must fight your way to the innermost sector and locate the technological menace.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32900_Text: I have taken the liberty of preparing an electrifying stage for you.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32901_Text: Meet one of my creations. You might find it a handful.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32902_Text: I will lay Garlond low, but first I must break you!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32903_Text: <pant> I will not suffer...to be in another's shadow!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32905_Text: Impressive! Now it is my turn!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32907_Text: Come, we shall see if you can finish what you have started.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32909_Text: That you should still stand... Very well, then!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32916_Text: Right, I'll examine the equipment for intelligence. Press onâ”€I'll let you know if I learn anything.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32917_Text: Well, well, would you look at this! It's the armor we borrowed for our mission at Castrum Centri!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32918_Text: If this isn't fate, I don't know what is! Go on, strap yourself in and raise hells!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32919_Text: If you will not yield, then you will be destroyed!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32920_Text: We need to make our way down. There ought to be a terminal for the lift up ahead.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_32921_Text: Here it is. If you'd care to take the van, I'll follow after I've had a look around.
